Package info.smart_tools.smartactors.core.wrapper_generator.annotations

  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    Counter
    Annotation for wrapper interface method that should be implemented as a counter method even if it's name doesn't start with "count".
    DefaultValue  
    DoNotImplement
    Annotation for the wrapper interface (default) method that should not be implemented by the wrapper generator.
    Getter
    Annotation for wrapper interface method that should be implemented as a getter method even if it's name doesn't start with "get", "is" or "has".
    InjectDefault  
    Setter
    Annotation for wrapper interface method that should be implemented as a setter method even if it's name doesn't start with "set".
    UseDefault  
    UseFieldName
